snippet.title: Inflatality PAX 2016 Trailer!
snippet.description:
More weapons! More arenas! Same derp! Inflatality returns to PAX Australia this year bringing fierce, derpy physics fighting featuring adorable inflatable wavers beating the crap out of each other.

Play it at the PAX Rising Pavillion in November.
